    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That makes sense. I think the \"polished\" part is where people usually get stuck though. Could you expand on that? Like, specifically when it comes to hair and grooming for both men and women? I want to make sure the advice covers how to avoid looking \"distracting\" or \"unprofessional\" in those intense settings.",
