      "content": "For men, hair should be neatly trimmed and styled in a conservative manner; anything overly trendy or long is distracting. Facial hair, if worn, must be meticulously maintained, not scruffy. Women's hair should be kept neat, whether worn up or down, avoiding excessive volume or bright colors. Makeup, if used, should be subtle and professional, designed to enhance features rather than draw attention to itself.",
